headline: If GTA VI Delivers, Take-Two Could Hit $300 in 2026
summary: Take-Two Interactive (NASDAQ: TTWO) has delivered a solid 2025, with shares up approximately 36% from their 52-week low of $177.35 and trading near recent highs.
